definitions.definition: A North American wildcat , Lynx rufus , having tufted ears and a short tail .

main_definition: A North American wildcat , Lynx rufus , having tufted ears and a short tail .

definitions.definition: A multi-purpose construction vehicle , akin to a smaller version of a front-end loader or a backhoe ( backhoe loader ), with a one-man caged control cabin .

main_definition: A multi-purpose construction vehicle , akin to a smaller version of a front-end loader or a backhoe ( backhoe loader ), with a one-man caged control cabin .
